channel.title: Is my STOCK computer good?
channel.description:
Okay, we'll I got a new computer a week or two ago, and I though I would post the specs just to see what you guys think of it.
Also this is a STOCK computer, I haven't changed ANYTHING internally.
Specs: - HP Laptop - 64-Bit operating system - 4gig Ram - 600gig Hard drive - Intel i7 Processor (8CPUs) 1.60GHz - ATI Mobility Radeon HD 5650 (Total approx. memory: 2773MB)
If I missed anything post it and I'll update, I'm not the smartest person when it comes to specs :S
